# Component Library

This document tracks reusable UI components used across IEXEL Club OS.

---

## Common Components

| Component | Status | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Button | Complete | Standard Club OS action buttons |
| Badge | Complete | Status labels and small UI labels |
| StatCard | Complete | Dashboard and event statistics |
| SectionCard | Complete | Reusable content section wrapper |
| SummaryCard | Legacy | Earlier summary component |
| CountdownCard | Complete | Countdown display component |

